              benar-benar terdapat tanda-tanda (kebesaran Allah) bagi<br />
              kaum yang berpikir.&rdquo;</span
            >

            <span class="lang-en"
              >&rdquo;And one of His signs is that He created for you spouses
              from among yourselves so that you may find comfort in them. And He
              has placed between you compassion and mercy. Surely in this are
              signs for people who reflect&rdquo;</span
