                        <span class="lang-mix">Save it to calendar</span>
                        <span class="lang-en">Save it to calendar</span>
                      </p>
                      <p
                        class="calendar-card__copy text-sm leading-relaxed text-charcoal/70 max-w-sm"
                      >
                        <span class="lang-mix"
                          >Simpan tanggal akad kami ke Google Calendar agar
                          tidak terlewat.</span
                        >
                        <span class="lang-en"
                          >Add our wedding ceremony to Google Calendar so the
                          date stays on your schedule.</span
                        >
                      </p>
                    </div>
                    <div
                      class="calendar-card__arrow w-10 h-10 rounded-full border border-charcoal/20 flex items-center justify-center transition-all duration-300 group-hover:bg-charcoal group-hover:border-charcoal"
