                        <span class="lang-mix">Detik</span>
                        <span class="lang-en">Sec</span>
                      </span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <div class="story-background">
        <div class="story-background__backdrop" aria-hidden="true">
          <img
            src="/assets/p1.webp"
            alt=""
            class="main-bg-image absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-center"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#007EA6] bg-gradient-to-b opacity-90 from-charcoal/40 via-charcoal/18 to-charcoal/32 transition-opacity duration-700"
          >
          </div>
        </div>

        <section
          class="content-card content-card--transparent py-32 px-6 text-center"
        >
          <div class="max-w-[56rem] mx-auto reveal">
            <div data-lang-block="mix" class="grid justify-items-center gap-4">
              <p class="story-intro__lead font-serif leading-relaxed">
                Dengan rahmat dan kasih sayang Allah SWT,
                <br />
                kami dengan bahagia mengumumkan pernikahan kami
              </p>

              <p class="story-intro__body leading-relaxed">
                Seiring kami menapaki perjalanan indah ini untuk menyempurnakan
                separuh agama, kami berdoa agar kehidupan kami bersama dipenuhi
                berkah yang tak terhingga dan ketenangan yang abadi. Berbagi
                momen suci ini bersama keluarga dan sahabat terkasih adalah
                harapan terbesar kami.
              </p>

              <p class="story-intro__body leading-relaxed">
                Kehadiran dan doa Anda akan menjadi kehormatan bagi kami di hari
                istimewa ini.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              data-lang-block="en"
              class="grid justify-items-center gap-4"
              hidden
            >
              <p class="story-intro__lead font-serif leading-relaxed">
                By the grace and mercy of Allah SWT,
                <br />
                we are delighted to announce our marriage
              </p>

              <p class="story-intro__body leading-relaxed">
                As we embark on this beautiful journey to complete half our
                faith, we pray our lives together will be filled with infinite
                blessings and lasting peace. Sharing this sacred milestone with
                our cherished friends and family is our greatest wish
              </p>

              <p class="story-intro__body leading-relaxed">
                Your presence and prayers would truly honor us on our special
                day
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Couple Introduction -->
        <section
          id="introduction"
          data-auto-scroll-section
          data-auto-scroll-align="start"
          class="content-card content-card--transparent py-32 px-6 z-[99]"
        >
          <div class="couple-shell desktop-shell max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="grid gap-28 md:gap-20">
              <div
                class="couple-card-group couple-card-group--reverse reveal"
                data-delay="80"
              >
                <figure
                  class="couple-card__image-frame couple-card__image-frame--single couple-card__image-frame--sherly couple-card__image-frame--enter-right"
