                      >&amp;</span
                    >
                    <span class="couple-card__meta-line"
                      >Mrs. Fatimah Umar Kuddah</span
                    >
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="couple-card-group reveal" data-delay="180">
                <figure
                  class="couple-card__image-frame couple-card__image-frame--single couple-card__image-frame--rian couple-card__image-frame--enter-left"
